{"tid":1449172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武定和理非","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:07.000Z","uid":96242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6d983fe90a5c6965ce3143cc891b309ac69047","tid":1449172,"uid":96242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"當初因為政府當和理非無到，所以好多人先由和理非進化成勇武<br />\n<br />\n但依家勇武嘅人多咗，但政府都係一樣唔理訴求，如果按依家走勢持續落去，只會有更多手足俾人拉<br />\n<br />\n小弟發夢嗰陣係前線，但見到每次當啲狗推進嘅時候，我地只能走，即使我地人多過佢地，都無人夠膽反打，如果繼續呢種方式勇武嘅，根本係單方面被打<br />\n<br />\n再加上已經證明咗前線係有鬼，去過前線都知周不時會有人走埋嚟叫人去邊去邊咁，如果嗰隻係鬼就係引導哂手足去俾圍捕<br />\n<br />\n所以係咪應該集中返一啲大型遊行/集會活動，而且唔好衝擊，一嚟唔好俾政府/對家有藉口譴責我地暴力，二嚟可以吸納更多和理非人參與<br />\n<br />\n如果全部轉返和理非遊行，當一有人煽風點火，就知邊啲係鬼，再用返呢一點幫之前被捕手足脫罪<br />\n<br />\n不過亦有憂慮嘅地方，即使轉返哂做和理非，政府都可以一樣唔理，如果去到咁無賴，可能真係只得焦土呢個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，俾到啲狗有喘息空間，可能會進行大規模搜捕，和理非亦都有機會俾人砌生豬肉<br />\n<br />\n總結，一係轉返哂做和理非，只繼續一啲大遊行/集會/罷工/杯葛狗隻或紅色企業行動<br />\n<br />\n如果要繼續勇武，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要係人多嘅時候反擊</span></span>，人少就要走，如果現場勇武手足唔多，就唔好戀戰留守<br />\n<br />\n覺得抗爭去到樽頸位有感而發，係香港有包袱嘅人太多，好難令所有人都完全豁出去抗爭"},{"pid":"fa16ae527d275216a0fdf5bbbdbf2676bb6e85b4","tid":1449172,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"認真答：Both"},{"pid":"4ef77a6dc0f071050136355762b9401d218888b1","tid":1449172,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"今日開始已經唔再需要理會道德加鎖，只有4個字： 後果自負 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}